                        <p>These events do not happen of their own accord and I am only too aware that an immense amount of hard work went into last night's dinner.  I am extremely proud of all our award winners; I am equally proud of the work that you did to enable us as a Force to congratulate them in the way that I think they deserved.</p>

                    </q>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
